description:
Precision's 650-pound poly trailer cart attaches to a mower or tractor just like its steel-bodied counterparts, but an added feature makes dumping loads of stone, soil, or yard waste even easier. The easy-dump release handle lets users tip the poly bed backwards while the tow bar remains in place. And that's not all - a handle allows you to switch between towing and pushing depending on the task. In addition, tool holders are molded into the poly body so rakes, spades, and clippers canbe stowed and retrieved. Homeowners, gardeners, landscape professionals, and farmers will all find loads of uses for this durable, dependable, and versatile cart.
Build Quality: Like Precision's steel-bed carts, this poly trailer cart is bolstered by a rugged steel undercarriage and tow bar. The single-piece hopper is made of heavy-duty poly designed for a lifetime of loading and unloading in the backyard or on the farm. Large 16" pneumatic tires are held in position by a 3/4-inch axle and all-steel wheels.

description:
6-Volt & 12-Volt & 24-Volt 50-Amp Smart Battery Charger
A multi-voltage charger - 6-volt (50-amps), 12-volt (50-amps), and 24-volt (25-amps) - for lead-acid automotive, marine, and deep-cycle batteries, including flooded, gel, AGM, and maintenance-free, plus lithium-ion.
Designed for pros who need absolute performance and uncompromising functionality. Featuring ultra- flexible silicone cabling - down to -40 degree F - with protective nylon breaded shielding for maximum protection against abrasion.
A dual-voltage power supply - 12-volt (50-amp) and 24-volt (25-amp) - to maintain constant power delivery without unwanted ripple, noise, and transient spikes during ECU flashing, reprogramming, and diagnostic testing.
An integrated thermal sensor detects the ambient temperature and alters the charge to eliminate over-charging in hot climates and under-charging in cold climates to maximize battery life and enable fast charging.
Detects batteries as low as 1-volt. Or use the all-new force mode that allows you to manually begin charging dead batteries down to zero volts.
Automatically detects battery sulfation and acid stratification to restore lost battery performance for stronger engine starts and extended battery life. Plus, cutting-edge battery repair modes for 6-volt, 12-volt, and 24-volt batteries.
6v/12v up to 2000 amp hours and 24v up to 1000 amp hours.
Size: 12.3" x 6.9" x 3.6"
name: 50A Battery Charger

Fill tire with air

description:
The X-Talker two-way radio provides reliable range for Clear Reception, Clear Transmission and ClearSound Quality. It comes with an array of features including Weather Alert Technology. License Free FRS Radio. Works with other FRS/GMRS radios.
36 Channels (14 Extra Channels) - Clear, crisp communication with easy button access
Xtreme Range* Up to 38 miles - Longer range communication in open areas with little or no obstruction
121 Privacy Codes - Gives you up to 2662 channel options to help you block other conversations
Weather Alert Radio w/Weather Scan - Automatically locks on to your local weather channel and alerts you to severe weather. NOAA Weather Alert and Weather Scan technology
Silent Operation - Turns off all tones for silent operation
Long battery life - (up to 15 hours) HI/LO Power Settings - Lets you adjust transmit power & conserve battery life
eVOX - Hands-Free Operation (9 levels) - Easy voice activation
Only available for sale in Canada, for the US see part # T71VP3

description:
The A-WL56M2C CabCAM WiRELESS System. The camera system comes with one 7" wide-angle color LCD monitor and two wireless 1/3" color CCD cameras. The 2.4 Ghz wireless system has a 200 yard barrier - free transmission range. The WL56M2C wireless system supports 12V automotive battery power allowing for easy installation. The WL56M2C wireless system can also be expanded to four camera capability by adding cameras WCCH1 & WCCH2.
200 yd barrier-free transmission range.
7" TFT LCD Wide-Angle Color Camera: High Resolution monitor with antenna. Four camera capability 2.4GHz wireless receiver with four channels. Supports 12V automotive battery.
The monitor includes: power indicator, remote receiving window, POWER button, MENU button, SEL button, channel selection, loudspeaker, support attaching slot and power supply terminal.
(2) 1/3" CCD Weatherproof Color Camera: One Channel 3 and one Channel 4 camera. Infrared Illuminators allow up to 32 feet of night visibility, image mirroring function, made to withstand off-road conditions, audio capabilities.
Each camera has an antenna and a power supply jack. Monitor works with 12 & 24 volt systems & cameras work with 12 volt systems but will require the AD520 voltage reducer for use with 24 volt systems.
Accessories: Base-Mounted Remote Antenna with 9.75' cord, Ball Swivel Mounting Bracket with Mounting Pad, U-Support Mounting Bracket with Thumb Screws, 6 Pin Power Wire Harness with Jack for AC/Cigarette Lighter/DC Adaptor, AC Power Adaptor,
Automotive Power Adapter, (3) 3.25' DC Adapters, Sunshield, RCA Cable, Full-Featured Remote Control.
This system can be expanded to support up to four cameras.
The A-WL56M2C analog system is the only unit currently offered with the capability of using multiple monitors (Fleet of trucks etc)

description:
*Only available for sale in the USA - GMRS License Required*
Improve communication efficiency on the farm, worksite or at play with the Midland MXT115AGVP3 MicroMobile Two Way radio kit. The kit contains the powerful MXT115 15-Watt GMRS Two-Way Radio and all the necessary hardware needed to install. The Midland MXT115AGVP3 works great in many applications with enclosed cabs such as tractors, combines, self-propelled sprayers, forage harvesters, industrial equipment, lawn & turf equipment, UTVs, semi and pickup trucks and many other applications
This radio boasts nearly quadruple the range of traditional CB radios. Additional features include 8GMRS repeater channels for extended transmission and reception ranges, a multi-colored LCD backlit display, NOAA weather alert channels and USB port for charging mobile devices. The bundle includes an MXT115 radio with mounting bracket, 3dB gain antenna, DC power adapter, antenna cable and mirror-mount bracket
Transmission distance may vary
Max - no line of sight obstruction (up to 50 miles)
Medium - partial line of sight obstruction (10 - 15 miles)
Short - major line of sight obstruction (5 - 10 miles)
*These are estimated distances based on field use and advertised ranges. Actual distance may vary*
Features: Radio Features: Full 15W Two-Way Radio, 8 repeater channels for increased communication range, 15 high power GMRS channels, 142 privacy codes, NOAA weather radio, radio mounting bracket, silent operation, channel scan, programmable squelch, keypad lock, monitor mode, keystroke tones, backlit display Antenna Features: 3dB gain antenna doubles the range of the radio, 6-Meter Antenna Cable & Bracket Mount Compatible with all Midland FRS/GMRS walkie talkies GMRS License Required Only available for sale in the USA
Includes: (1) MXT115 MicroMobileï¿½ Two-Way GMRS Radio (1) MXTA23 Bracket Mount (1) MXTA24 6-Meter Antenna Cable (1) MXTA25 3dB Antenna
name: Two Way Radio, Midland Micromobile Bundle

No need to break the bead or remove the tire from the rim. When you insert the QuikStem into a rim and tighten down the nut the rubber grommet expands to more than a third of the size of the rim hole creating a seal.
Remove or drive in old valve stem
Push QuikStem into hole from out side of rim
Tighten nut firmly snug
Fill tire with air
For .453" stem hole
Not recommended for on-highway vehicles
2 pack
name: QuickStem Tire Valve Stem, Long, For .453" Stem Hole (2 pk)

The MICHELIN X TWEEL TURF CASTER is also a single unit that replaces the tire/wheel/valve assembly. Get maximum performance for your machine by using TWEEL on both your rear and front tires. TWEEL CASTER is maintenance free, lasts longer than traditional tires and ensures an even cut and enhanced operator comfort.
The TWEEL CASTER is designed for optimal balance of mass and compression in order to provide the best cutting experience. Adding TWEEL drive and caster wheels enhances the performance of the mowers suspension providing for a softer ride. This can give the sensation that the machine is lighter or floating compared to a mower with traditional pneumatic or semi-pneumatic tires.

description:
QuickStem Push In Tire Valve Stem is designed to quickly replace torn, damaged or leaking tire stems. Just push in, tighten the nut and inflate. No need to break the bead or remove the tire from the rim. When you insert the QuikStem into a rim and tighten down the nut the rubber grommet expands to more than a third of the size of the rim hole creating a seal.
Remove or drive in old valve stem
Push QuikStem into hole from outside of rim
Tighten nut firmly snug
Fill tire with air
For .625" stem hole
Not recommended for on-highway vehicles
2 pack
name: QuikStem Tire Valve Stem, Long, For .625" Stem Hole (2 pk)

description:
4-In-1 Implement Cable is designed to connect multiple wired CabCAM cameras (up to 4).
It can be used on a variety of machines, but is designed to ease installation of cameras on air seeder applications.
It includes a short 4-way splitter cable (C4SPL) to connect up to 4 cameras on the air cart, a 32' (10m) extension cable (C10CE) for across the seed tool, and a 32' (10m) tractor cable with 4-way splitter (C104M) to connect to camera inputs on the monitor.
The cables in this kit can be purchased individually as well, see associated items.
Includes: (1) Short 4-way splitter cable (C4SPL), a 32' (10m) extension cable (C10CE) and a 32' (10m) tractor cable with 4-way splitter (C104M). These items are also offered individually, see associated parts.

description:
The VS1CWL wired camera is a waterproof, color camera with audio. The VS1CWL has 110 degrees of viewing angle and white LED illuminators. The VS1CWL also has mirroring capability and able to withstand off-road conditions.
The white LED illuminators allow you to light up the area you are viewing up to 32', allowing colors to be visible.
The white LED illuminators are on at all times, even when the monitor is turned off. In order for the white LED illuminators to go off, power to the monitor needs to be removed.
Because the LED lights are on at all times, it is recommended to use this type of camera in special applications only, such as air-seeder tanks or other constantly dark areas.
Dim A (1): For use with wired CabCAM systems

name: CabCAM Camera, 110ï¿½, White LED

description:
Serious yard work calls for serious tools, which is why homeowners and commercial landscapers turn to Precision and its line of professional-grade tow behinds. This spreader holds 200 pounds in its heavy-duty plastic hopper and broadcasts with a 10 to 12-foot spread pattern. A rugged steel frame holds the hopper and the durable metal gears which are housed in a metal gearbox. Large, 15-inch treaded turf tires provide a smooth ride across rough ground and won't damage soft sod or new plantings like solid plastic wheels can. From the seat of your tractor of choice you can control the spread radius and turn the spreader on and off via direct rod control. A durable rain cover fits snugly and protects material in the hopper from moisture. Attaches to all brands of riding mowers, tractors and ATVs.
Build Quality: Precision's tow behind broadcast spreaders are made with fewer parts than the competitors use, so they're easy to put together and will have you spreading seed or nutrients about a half an hour after opening the box. Heavy-duty 1-1/4-inch powder-coated steel tubing supports the rugged plastic hopper and ends at the universal hitch with pin.
Capacity: 200 lbs.
Body/Frame: Heavy-duty plastic body and 1-1/4" powder-coated steel tubing frame
Wheels: Steel
Tires: 15" pneumatic tires
Assembled Size: 30"H x 45"D x 34"W
Spread Pattern/Swath: 10'-12'
Gears: Metal with grease zerk
Hole Design: 1 hole
Flow Control: Direct Rod
name: 200 LB. COMMERCIAL TOW BEHIND BROADCAST SPREADER

description:
6-Volt & 12-Volt & 24-Volt 25-Amp Smart Battery Charger
A multi-voltage charger - 6-volt (25-amps), 12-volt (25-amps), and 24-volt (12.5-amps) - for lead-acid automotive, marine, and deep-cycle batteries, including flooded, gel, AGM, and maintenance-free, plus lithium-ion.
Designed for pros who need absolute performance and uncompromising functionality. Featuring ultra- flexible silicone cabling - down to -40 degree C - with protective nylon breaded shielding for maximum protection against abrasion.
A dual-voltage power supply - 12-volt (25-amp) and 24-volt (12.5-amp) - to maintain constant power delivery without unwanted ripple, noise, and transient spikes during ECU flashing, reprogramming, and diagnostic testing.
An integrated thermal sensor detects the ambient temperature and alters the charge to eliminate over-charging in hot climates and under-charging in cold climates to maximize battery life and enable fast charging.
Detects batteries as low as 1-volt. Or use the all-new force mode that allows you to manually begin charging dead batteries down to zero volts.
Automatically detects battery sulfation and acid stratification to restore lost battery performance for stronger engine starts and extended battery life. Plus, cutting-edge battery repair modes for 6-volt, 12-volt, and 24-volt batteries.
6v/12v up to 1000 amp hours and 24v up to 500 amp hours.
Size: 9.3" x 5.1" x 3.0"
name: 25A Battery Charger

description:
QuickStem Push In Tire Valve Stem is designed to quickly replace torn, damaged or leaking tire stems. Just push in, tighten the nut and inflate. No need to break the bead or remove the tire from the rim. When you insert the QuikStem into a rim and tighten down the nut the rubber grommet expands to more than a third of the size of the rim hole creating a seal.
Remove or drive in old valve stem
Push QuikStem into hole from outside of rim
Tighten nut firmly snug
Fill tire with air
For .625" stem hole
Not recommended for on-highway vehicles
2 pack
name: QuikStem Tire Valve Stem, Short, For .625" Stem Hole (2 pk)
